{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/how-to-fix-logo-empty-space","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1485,"date":"2022-03-01T17:38:14","date_gmt":"2022-03-01T17:38:14","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1485"},"modified":"2022-03-01T17:52:57","modified_gmt":"2022-03-01T17:52:57","slug":"how-to-fix-logo-empty-space","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/how-to-fix-logo-empty-space/","title":{"rendered":"How to fix empty space around any Shopify theme&#8217;s logo"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>After much work, your website&#8217;s logo is finally done and it looks great. You&#8217;re excited to upload it to your website, and when you finally do so, you notice a problem: it is either way too small or with lots of space surrounding it. <br><br>It&#8217;s natural to assume it could be something easily fixed with a piece of code (and sometimes it could indeed be the case), but more often than not the issue is not related to code at all, it&#8217;s related to the image itself. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-understanding-the-problem\">Understanding the problem</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Take a look at the following example:<br></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"514\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image-1200x514.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1488\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image-1200x514.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image-850x364.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image-768x329.png 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image.png 1322w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Although the logo per se looks ok, it is looking really small when loaded to the website. And, when we increase the logo&#8217;s width, you can notice the header&#8217;s height gets obnoxiously large:<br><br></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"671\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image-3-1200x671.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1498\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image-3-1200x671.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image-3-850x475.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image-3-768x429.png 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image-3.png 1288w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So, what is the problem there? It&#8217;s actually quite simple: the white space surrounding the image is adding extra padding to the website. This can not (well, rather <em>should<strong> </strong></em>not<em><strong>)</strong></em> be fixed with code. You must trim the white space around it. <br><br>In this particular example the logo&#8217;s background is white, but it could be of any color or even transparent, it would still be adding unnecessary space. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to actually fix the problem</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To fix it you just have to trim all the empty space surrounding your logo with an image editing software. For the sake of simplicity, in this tutorial I&#8217;ll be using the <a href=\"https://www.iloveimg.com/crop-image?source=ezfycode\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">I Love Image&#8217;s online image cropper</a>. It is free and very simple to use. Just upload your logo to the website, trim the white space around it and download the new image. Here is how our logo looks now without any white space around it:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"619\" height=\"444\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1492\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And here is how it looks in our header:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"632\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image-2-1200x632.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1494\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image-2-1200x632.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image-2-850x448.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image-2-768x404.png 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image-2.png 1358w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This is how you can fix your logo&#8217;s spacing without touching any code. You may also be interested in some other tutorials:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/add-slideshow-shopify-no-apps\">&#8211; How to make slideshow images stop cutting off</a><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/UKO9ViFXaWQ\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"\">&amp;lt;br>&amp;lt;a href=&#8221;https://ezfycode.com/blog/collection-with-tabs-shopify-section-tutorial&#8221; target=&#8221;_blank&#8221; rel=&#8221;noreferrer noopener&#8221;>- Add a collection tabs slider to any store (copy/paste, no apps, blazing fast)&amp;lt;/a>&amp;lt;iframe width=&#8221;560&#8243; height=&#8221;315&#8243; src=&#8221;https://www.youtube.com/embed/MuD0FgqENoc&#8221; title=&#8221;YouTube video player&#8221; frameborder=&#8221;0&#8243; allow=&#8221;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share&#8221; allowfullscreen=&#8221;&#8221;>&amp;amp;amp;lt;br>&amp;amp;amp;lt;a href=&#8221;https://ezfycode.com/blog/how-to-disable-right-click-image-and-text-copying-without-apps&#8221;>- Disable right click, image and text copying and improve your store&#8217;s security&amp;amp;amp;lt;/a></iframe><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/collection-with-tabs-shopify-section-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; How to add a collection with tabs section to any theme (copy/paste, no apps, blazing fast)</a><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/MuD0FgqENoc\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"\"><br><br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><br></h3>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Understand why your logo may be looking smaller than it actually is and learn simple ways to fix it.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1507,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[9],"tags":[206],"image_alt":"","featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/white-space-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/white-space-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/white-space-1200x675.png","categories_names":["Blog"],"acf":[],"tag_names":["all themes"],"featured_image_url":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/white-space.png","featured_image_url_alt":"","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1485"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=1485"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1485/revisions"}],"pre